WEBVTT

34:25.830 --> 34:26.830 line:80%
Don't return it.

34:27.430 --> 34:29.910 line:80%
Father must have felt sorry
for your chapped hands

34:29.910 --> 34:31.439 line:80%
and prepared it for you.

34:31.510 --> 34:33.300 line:80%
Our father wouldn't be so silly

34:33.330 --> 34:34.860 line:80%
to buy such useless things.

34:35.200 --> 34:36.760 line:80%
I'll return it and buy you candy.
